caption.text:
This is how I reached 4 million+ accounts last month👇

I post three times a day on average. Most of the time, I would say 60–70% of my content consists of new ideas, where an idea is a combination of a topic and a type of video.

For example, I can create a video about how to gain followers. 

I can share the same tip on the topic in the form of a carousel, a 60-second talking head video, or a pointing video that is 2 to 5 seconds long with a call to action to read the caption. In the caption, I can elaborate on the topic.

All three different types of videos with the same topic are different content ideas. So, the majority of my content is new content ideas.

However, every fifth or sixth video for me goes viral, meaning the combination of topic and type of video gets me more than 100k views, where part of it or most of it comes from non-followers.

What I do next is take this viral idea and re-create it multiple times—4 to 5 times over the next 2 to 3 weeks. When I re-create it, I can re-create either the topic or the type of video.

For example, if a carousel about gaining followers goes viral, over the next two weeks I can re-create it 4–5 times with different types of videos on the same topic, providing the same advice that I provided in the carousel. 

Alternatively, I can create more carousels about other similar topics while maintaining the structure of the original carousel because that structure worked well for me in the viral one.

If you use this strategy consistently, re-creating your top performers multiple times each week while also testing new ideas, it will double or triple your growth.

Last month, every second time I added a transition hook to my reel, it went viral!

Comment the words CRAZY HOOKS, and I’ll send you a list of popular hooks you can use for your content. 

Add them to the very beginning of your reel to get more views.

SEO friendly captions 👇

Hashtags are gone. SEO now is the thing to gain quality followers with!

The more keywords you use now in your caption they more likely your posts reach right audience. 

Technically they work same way like hashtags. They make your content searcheable on the platform and also push your content to new audience.

But instead of having random 10 keywords that nobody will read you can have a good valuable caption using these 5-10 keywords that will convert!

As well as captions make your usernames or account’s name SEO friendly to get more leads and sales

If I type in the search on Instagram “barber NYC” I’ll see only the ones who have these keywords in their username or name of their account (not bio though)

That’s how they get customers and new followers 

Those barbers in NYC who don’t have those keywords in their username or name of their accounts will not show up in the list so they limit their growth and new requests from potential clients

Comment “OPTIMIZE” and get my new training on how to Optimize your Instagram account for more followers growth

It includes:
✅ Bio optimisation

✅ Pinned posts strategy

The training is free if you comment me the word “OPTIMIZE”

caption.text:
New IG growth strategy unlocked 🔓👇

Growing ORGANICALLY on Instagram is not easy, and it’s not fast.

It can take you up to 6-12 months to build the community you want, get hundreds of inbound leads monthly, and make multiple 5-6 figures without paying for ads.

But today, I’m sharing with you a new strategy that will help you grow faster!

The strategy helped me reach almost 10 million accounts in the last 90 days and grow my account from 1.3 million followers to 1.4 million.

Most importantly, we started executing this strategy with some of our DFY clients, and it works really well!

Take a look at it now to implement it by EOW and get more views right away!

The strategy is called RECREATE WHAT WORKS.

We post reels to test ideas. Once you have one reel that «goes viral,» you need to recreate it 4-5 times in the next 2-3 weeks to get even more views with this proven reel idea.

The more viral videos you have, the more recreated viral videos you have, and the more good content you post, the more you grow.

Only our paid clients have access to this training

Comment FASTER and I’ll dm you this new training for free 🔥

caption.text:
Growing ORGANICALLY on Instagram is not easy, and it’s not fast.

It can take you up to 6-12 months to build the community you want, get hundreds of inbound leads monthly, and make multiple 5-6 figures without paying for ads.

But today, I’m sharing with you a new strategy that will help you grow faster!

The strategy helped me reach almost 10 million accounts in the last 90 days and grow my account from 1.3 million followers to 1.4 million.

Most importantly, we started executing this strategy with some of our DFY clients, and it works really well!

Take a look at it now to implement it by EOW and get more views right away!

The strategy is called RECREATE WHAT WORKS.

We post reels to test ideas. Once you have one reel that “goes viral,” you need to recreate it 4-5 times in the next 2-3 weeks to get even more views with this proven reel idea.

The more viral videos you have, the more recreated viral videos you have, and the more good content you post, the more you grow.

Only our paid clients have access to this training

Comment FASTER and I’ll dm you this new training for free 🔥
